com.jaspersoft.android.sdk.client.async.task

Class JsAsyncTask<Params,Result>

  • java.lang.Object
    • android.os.AsyncTask<Params,java.lang.String,Result>
      • com.jaspersoft.android.sdk.client.async.task.JsAsyncTask<Params,Result>
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    JsRestAsyncTask
    Deprecated. 
    Use BaseRequest instead.

    @Deprecated
public abstract class JsAsyncTask<Params,Result>
extends android.os.AsyncTask<Params,java.lang.String,Result>

    Declaration of the JsAsyncTask which is subclass of Android core AsyncTask abstract class that enables proper and easy use of the Android UI thread. JsAsyncTask enables of Progress dialog integration due of encapsulating of Progress tracker.

    Since:
    1.0
